{"tid":2185634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］有無人體溫好易過高？","createTime":"2020-09-02T11:28:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T14:14:29.000Z","uid":85205,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7c4bf0d9c51988f01c7b5ea8b43208958e2e90eb","tid":2185634,"uid":85205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"天氣熱到痴線，戴住口罩又焗<br />\n唔知點解個人嘅體溫好易會去到37.4，好多時去街舖量體溫都過高，每次量體溫過高部機響到防盜器咁，個個望過黎真係好柒，商場舖就無事36.5左右<br />\n<br />\n今朝入街舖量咗次，過高，之後晏晝再去街舖之前去咗隔離7仔涼咗陣冷氣先入去<br />\n宜家每次入舖頭量體溫都好緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚其他人誤會我發燒，有無得搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f17f4f2fa149c177102f217c9f6b41013f0d4e","tid":2185634,"uid":85205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實係咪應該開係健康台"},{"pid":"2b9766111e8166a24e6b4575611ace251782dd27","tid":2185634,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"好認真，用退熱貼啦"},{"pid":"9a4c1c3d2be4b4ba4e30789816c5b285a752288b","tid":2185634,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:31:11.000Z","msg":"你一定好瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f31a9e4f43c1bbe0534ce6fd4e871e9800c0264","tid":2185634,"uid":260744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:31:24.000Z","msg":"唔好害人啦，入醫院啦"},{"pid":"8fa81d68ee5be03f6fdb32540be0d9da17fbb57f","tid":2185634,"uid":55851,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:33:01.000Z","msg":"即係發燒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快撚啲去睇醫生<img src